OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,FA police group has reacted with fury
OL,7,Fat the "nonsensical" decision that the
OL,8,Fpolice marksman who shot Chris Kaba
OL,9,Fshould face a disciplinary hearing and
OL,10,Fcould be sacked.
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police officer Martyn
OL,13,FBlake, 41, shot the 24-year-old in
OL,14,FStreatham, south-east London, in
OL,15,FSeptember 2022 after Mr Kaba tried to
OL,16,Fram his way past police cars that had
OL,17,Fhemmed him in.
