OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,FHe was cleared of murder over the
OL,7,Fshooting in October, but on Wednesday
OL,8,Fwatchdog the Independent Office for
OL,9,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) said he will
OL,10,Fstill have to face gross misconduct
OL,11,Fproceedings.
OL,13,FIOPC director Amanda Rowe said: "This
OL,14,Fis a decision we have taken based on
OL,15,Fexamining all the evidence, views of
OL,16,Fall parties and by applying the
OL,17,Fthresholds set out in legislation and
OL,18,Fguidance which govern our work.
OL,26,@uD@aOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
