OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,F"The legal test for deciding whether
OL,7,Fthere is a case to answer is low ` is
OL,8,Fthere sufficient evidence upon which,
OL,9,Fon the balance of probabilities, a
OL,10,Fdisciplinary panel could make a
OL,11,Ffinding of misconduct. This has been
OL,12,Fmet and therefore we need to follow
OL,13,Fthe legal process.
OL,15,F"We appreciate that the Home Office is
OL,16,Fcarrying out a review of the legal
OL,17,Ftest for the use of force in
OL,18,Fmisconduct cases, however, we must
OL,19,Fapply the law as it currently stands."
