OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police bosses had argued
OL,7,Fthat the evidence against Mr Blake had
OL,8,Fbeen "tested significantly" during the
OL,9,Ftrial and that the IOPC should
OL,10,Freconsider whether he should face a
OL,11,Fdisciplinary hearing.
OL,13,FMatt Cane, general secretary of the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police Federation that
OL,15,Frepresents rank and file officers in
OL,16,Fthe force, said: "This is frankly a
OL,17,Fnonsensical ruling by the IOPC that
OL,18,Fwill shock police officers across
OL,19,FLondon and indeed the country.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@[O]xD@ROU
