OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F403A1746092956
OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,F"Police officers should not have their
OL,7,Flivelihoods or liberty put at risk for
OL,8,Fperforming what unequivocally, as has
OL,9,Fbeen found in a court of law, is their
OL,10,Flawful and appropriate function.
OL,12,F"And yet putting this brave officer on
OL,13,Ftrial for murder ` as astonishing as
OL,14,Fthat was ` was not enough for the
OL,15,FIOPC. Being cleared unanimously by a
OL,16,Fjury who heard all the evidence was
OL,17,Fnot enough for the IOPC. They have now
OL,18,Fdecided to put him and his family
OL,19,Fthrough more torment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
