OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,F"This is not accountability. This is
OL,7,Fnot in the public interest. This is
OL,8,Fnot right or fair or just.
OL,10,F"We will be vigorously defending the
OL,11,Factions of Sgt Blake at any conduct
OL,12,Fproceedings."
OL,14,FIf the hearing finds he committed
OL,15,Fgross misconduct he could face the
OL,16,Fsack.
