OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,FOn the night Mr Kaba died, police
OL,7,Fbegan following the Audi Q8 that he
OL,8,Fwas driving because it had been used
OL,9,Fas a getaway car in a shooting in
OL,10,FBrixton, south London, the night
OL,11,Fbefore.
OL,13,FThey did not know who was driving the
OL,14,Fcar at the time, although it later
OL,15,Femerged Mr Kaba was a core member of
OL,16,Fone of London's most dangerous street
OL,17,Fgangs and was accused of being
OL,18,Finvolved in two shootings in the week
OL,19,Fbefore he died.
