OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Met Police Assistant
OL,7,FCommissioner Laurence Taylor, using
OL,8,Fthe cypher NX121 that was given to Mr
OL,9,FBlake before a judge ruled he could be
OL,10,Fpublicly named, said: "NX121 made a
OL,11,Fsplit-second decision on what he
OL,12,Fbelieved was necessary to protect his
OL,13,Fcolleagues and London and a jury
OL,14,Funanimously decided that was an
OL,15,Fhonestly held belief and the force
OL,16,Fused was reasonable.
OL,18,F"However, the IOPC has now determined
OL,19,Fthat NX121 has a case to answer for
OL,20,Fhis use of force and has directed us
OL,21,Fto hold a gross misconduct hearing.
OL,26,@rD@WOUzD@AOU
