OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,F"We know another lengthy process will
OL,7,Ffall heavily on the shoulders of NX121
OL,8,Fand more widely our firearms officers,
OL,9,Fwho continue to bravely and tirelessly
OL,10,Fpolice the streets of London every day
OL,11,Fto protect the public."
OL,13,FA chief officer from an outside force
OL,14,Fwill be asked to chair the
OL,15,Fdisciplinary hearing, which will be
OL,16,Fheld in due course, the force said.
OL,18,FIn a statement issued through the
OL,19,Fcharity Inquest, Mr Kaba's family
OL,20,Fwelcomed the IOPC's decision.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]
