OL,3,CFury as armed officer who shot Chris
OL,4,CKaba to face disciplinary hearing
OL,6,F"We hope this leads to him being
OL,7,Fremoved from the Met Police," they
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"What Martyn Blake did was deeply
OL,11,Fwrong. We are still so devastated to
OL,12,Fhave lost Chris ` this should never
OL,13,Fhave happened.
OL,15,F"The fact that the Met promoted Martyn
OL,16,FBlake after the verdict only deepened
OL,17,Four pain and showed a complete
OL,18,Fdisregard for our loss.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@]O]rD@AOUwD@AOU
