OL,6,F"Martyn Blake should not be allowed to
OL,7,Fremain a police officer. He should
OL,8,Flose his job."
OL,10,FDeborah Coles, director of Inquest,
OL,11,Fcalled it "reprehensible" that the Met
OL,12,Fhad to be directed to hold a
OL,13,Fdisciplinary hearing.
OL,15,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp said
OL,16,Fhe was "deeply disappointed" by the
OL,17,Fwatchdog's decision.
