OL,6,FWriting on X, he said: "We need to
OL,7,Fsupport police officers who do
OL,8,Fdifficult things to protect the
OL,9,Fpublic, provided they act in
OL,10,Faccordance with the law, as a jury
OL,11,Ffound this officer did.
OL,13,F"This has hung over Sergeant Blake for
OL,14,Ftoo long. I think the IOPC has got
OL,15,Fthis wrong."
